WEBVTT

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:05.844
[Aibileen] Eighteen people
died in Jackson that day.

00:00:07.133 --> 00:00:09.101
Ten white and eight black.

00:00:10.052 --> 00:00:13.022
- [Aibileen murmuring]
- [Mae Mobley fretting]

00:00:13.180 --> 00:00:17.560
God don't pay no mind to color once
He decide to set a tornado loose.

00:00:17.726 --> 00:00:20.650
Aibee's here, honey.

00:00:20.813 --> 00:00:22.360
Aibee's here.

